# ── ARCHITECTURAL NOTE ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Per AI SAFE2 v3.0 CP.5.MCP-9, the Agentic Control Plane (CP.4) MUST enforce
# the isolation boundary at the orchestration layer. Per-tool sanitization is a
# defense-in-depth measure, not a substitute for CP.4 enforcement.
